                  o long as they make it not evident, that the scandall of the Ceremonies, which we object, is no active or faulty scandall; as long they can not object the scandall of Non-conformity to us; because if the scandall (which is to be avoided) be in their practising of the Ceremonies, it can not be in our refusing of them.
