                  Est. 9. 20. 21. were established by Mordecai a Prophet.
               2. We have else-where made it evident, that the dayes of Purim by their first Institution were only dayes of civill joy and solemnity: and that the Feast of the Dedication was not lawfully instituted. d Supra Cap. 6.
               
